Notes:
"2018 was a steady year for InterConnection as we worked to increase community awareness surrounding our mission to bridge the digital divide by providing affordable refurbished computers and high-speed internet to underserved communities in Seattle and across the U.S.

The digital divide is the economic and social inequality regarding access to information and communication technologies."; 

"The average American household produces 176 pounds of e-waste every year, but thanks to committed supporters like you, we were able to prevent over 1 million pounds of e-waste from ending up in landfills"
